data.description: **Price just reduced** Nice Arlington property available to make your own. Freshly painted inside and out; New LVP in main living areas. Updated kitchen with new appliances, white cabinets and granite countertops. Hall bath updated with large soaking tub and separate shower; some areas of the master bath updated as well, just needs your finishing touches. 3 nice sized bedrooms with newer flooring. Nice bonus room in the back leading out into the back yard.  2 car garage and nice patio-covered front porch. HVAC 2022, Water Heater 2022, Roof 2016.  Cast iron plumbing removed less than 2 years ago. Professional Photos coming soon!
